'''Carol Nixon''' is President of [[Utah Families Foundation]], Utah Arts Council director and the first female to serve as chief of staff to an Utah governor.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.deseretnews.com/article/258085/UTAH-WOMAN-MAKES-HISTORY-AS-BANGERTERS-CHIEF-OF-STAFF.html?pg=all|title=UTAH WOMAN MAKES HISTORY AS BANGERTER'S CHIEF OF STAFF|website=DeseretNews.com|access-date=2016-03-10}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=UTAH MARKS ANOTHER ARTS `FIRST' WITH ENDOWMENT|url=http://www.deseretnews.com/article/89013/UTAH-MARKS-ANOTHER-ARTS-FIRST-WITH-ENDOWMENT.html?pg=all}}</ref>  She is the wife of [[William L. Nixon]].

